{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSMediaRule","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSS_Object_Model\">CSS Object Model <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule\"><code>CSSMediaRule</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule/media\"><code>media</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu CSSOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSS\"><code>CSS</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframeRule\"><code>CSSKeyframeRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSKeyframesRule\"><code>CSSKeyframesRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSNamespaceRule\"><code>CSSNamespaceRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSPageRule\"><code>CSSPageRule</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSRuleList\"><code>CSSRuleList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleDeclaration\"><code>CSSStyleDeclaration</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleRule\"><code>CSSStyleRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSStyleSheet\"><code>CSSStyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSSupportsRule\"><code>CSSSupportsRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CaretPosition\"><code>CaretPosition</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Screen\"><code>Screen</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheet\"><code>StyleSheet</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StyleSheetList\"><code>StyleSheetList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TransitionEvent\"><code>TransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die <strong>CSSMediaRule</strong> ist eine Schnittstelle, die eine einzelne CSS-Regel darstellt. Sie implementiert die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-Schnittstelle und somit auch die <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>- sowie die <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a>-Schnittstelle mit einem Typwert von <code>4</code>&nbsp;(<code>CSSRule.MEDIA_RULE</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die Syntax wird mittels der&nbsp;<a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/2006/webapi/WebIDL/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WebIDL</a> definiert.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">interface CSSMediaRule : CSSConditionRule {\n    readonly attribute MediaList media;\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Als eine <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, und somit der <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a>, implementiert die <code>CSSMediaRule</code> auch gleichzeitig die Eigenschaften dieser Schnittstellen. Darüber hinaus hat sie die folgende spezielle Eigenschaft<code>:</code></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"cssmediarule.media_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule/media\"><code>CSSMediaRule.media</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></dt>\n <dd>Definiert&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaList\"><code>MediaList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, welches das zugedachte Zielmedium für die Style-Informationen wiedergibt.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methoden","title":"Methoden","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wie eine <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und daher eine <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSGroupingRule\"><code>CSSGroupingRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> als auch eine <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSRule\"><code>CSSRule</code></a>, implementiert <code>CSSMediaRule</code> auch die Methoden dieser Schnittstelle. Sie selbst hat keine speziellen Methoden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-conditional-3/#the-cssmediarule-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Conditional Rules Module Level&nbsp;3<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CSSMediaRule' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Anwärter Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Als Ableitung von &nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSConditionRule\"><code>CSSConditionRule</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#the-cssmediarule-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Object Model (CSSOM)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CSSMediaRule' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Keine Abweichungen von &nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSMediaRule\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CSSMediaRule' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Veraltet</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibilität","title":"Browser Kompatibilität&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Merkmal</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td>45.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span> [1]</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Merkmal</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE&nbsp;Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>45.0</td>\n   <td>17.0 (17) [1]</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>45.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Das Setzen des Werts von&nbsp;<code>conditionText</code>&nbsp;in Gecko ist nur ab Firefox&nbsp;20 möglich.</p>","titleAsText":"Browser Kompatibilität "}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"},{"text":"Methoden","id":"methoden"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität&nbsp;","id":"browser_kompatibilität"}],"summary":"Die CSSMediaRule ist eine Schnittstelle, die eine einzelne CSS-Regel darstellt. Sie implementiert die CSSConditionRule (en-US)-Schnittstelle und somit auch die CSSGroupingRule (en-US)- sowie die CSSRule-Schnittstelle mit einem Typwert von 4 (CSSRule.MEDIA_RULE).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"CSSMediaRule","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/cssmediarule","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/cssmediarule/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/CSSMediaRule","title":"CSSMediaRule"}],"pageTitle":"CSSMediaRule - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}